To build run:

	make

To install:

	make install

		(as root)

To uninstall:

	make uninstall

		(as root)

Usage:

	g15date
		Displays time (analogue clock) and date.
	g15date -d
		Displays time (digital) and date.

-----
NOTE:	The g15daemon must be running.
-----

Version:
	0.2 - Early development!

Email dean.birch0@gmail.com with bugs, suggestions, or just let me know that someone is actually using this package!
